    "description": "Command thousands of cats on their journey to find a new home! Catastrophic Cat Command is an arcade-style game where you manage multiple mini-games at once! It’s the perfect game for a quick 5-minute break from work!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are currently a total of 12 mini-games that take only a few seconds to complete. You’ll start with only one game active, but every 60 seconds, a new game spawns that you have to manage simultaneously. It gets stressful pretty fast, so bring a sweatband.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game starts in Tutorial Mode, where you can try out all available mini-games in a less stressful environment. Once you’re familiar with all the games, you can start the main mode by pressing Enter. Here, you’ll try to save as many cats as you can until you inevitably fail.",
